{"tid":947703,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)天眼救未來 新舊宇宙威龍 烈探追擊","createTime":"2018-12-19T12:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T19:54:29.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5648b2da00677ecbebeb5576d1bad6e741ab72","tid":947703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:57:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=67e68e4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f1d9c3d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9ce2d848\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/2/2e/Next_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F2%2F2e%2FNext_poster.jpg&h=f746042c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a5/Total-recall-poster-banner-image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa5%2FTotal-recall-poster-banner-image.jpg&h=f5acd162&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/87/1990-Total-recall-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F87%2F1990-Total-recall-poster.jpg&h=a4715ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d1/Jack_Reacher_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd1%2FJack_Reacher_poster.jpg&h=effc1eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.克里斯&middot;強森擁有可以看見未來，並以行動改變未來的能力，不過擁有特殊能力的他，受不了政府和醫學機構的檢查，於是隱藏起來混在拉斯維加斯的小賭場賭博和變魔術維生。<br />\n不過此時有FBI幹員寇莉&middot;佛瑞斯前來找尋克里斯&middot;強森，原來為了要避免恐怖組織炸掉洛杉磯核能電廠的陰謀，佛瑞斯必須盡速找到強森並且改變這件可怕的未來<br />\n<br />\n2.二十一世紀末期，全球爆發生化武器戰爭，所遺留下來的致命毒氣布滿了世界各處，造成地球只剩下部分區域能夠居住，其中兩個最大的地區為「不列顛聯邦」（歐洲）以及「殖民地」（澳洲）。當時來往兩地之飛機已不復存在，只能靠穿過地心的「天梯」來往。後來，不列顛聯邦因爲人口氾濫開始爭奪殖民地的土地擁有權，殖民地相較於聯邦政府的優越而成為被壓榨的一方。一群不滿殖民地遭政府壓榨的人成立了「反抗軍」，表面上是一個多次遭政府指控為發動多起爆炸恐怖攻擊的元兇，實際上是一群幫助殖民地來對抗聯邦政府的反抗組織<br />\n<br />\n3.故事發生在2084年。Douglas Quaid是一個建築工人，每天都會做陪伴一個女人去火星旅遊，卻最終遇險身亡的噩夢，第二天早上都會在妻子Lori的親吻與安慰中醒來。一次他在地鐵上看到一個Rekall公司的廣告，這個公司可以把內存植入人腦，使人可以虛擬冒險，所以他決定購買一個在火星上的虛擬歷險，在這個歷險中他會扮演一個間諜。Quaid的同事告訴他Rekall具有風險，植入手術失敗可能造成類似腦白質切除術的後果，受害者會受到永久性的精神傷害。Quaid猶豫了一陣，但是卻忽視了這個警告<br />\n<br />\n4.美國賓夕法尼亞州匹茲堡市一個平靜的小鎮，一如往常的早晨，五個人照常過日子，卻慘遭隨機射殺。所有證據都指向一個人：槍法神準的殺手，他前身是軍人，訓練有素的狙擊手。一個符合條件的嫌犯很快地遭到逮捕與拘提，但經過漫長的訊問之後警方卻問不出任何事。這名嫌犯只用手寫下了一個神祕的要求：「給我傑克&middot;李奇」。誰是傑克？這問題令人費解<br />\n<br />\n9 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8237c340\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=340eb9fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c0822e86f6aa63cba0d55fc3f6bbb12922b1fd","tid":947703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983e672d328a4c58872280f07206baecd43af2e6","tid":947703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4956d2b3475ca7da5b7b57b0ba70f5bd4248c2","tid":947703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af14eb3aed80ffb839395321ff85d4e8e04ba0d","tid":947703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203eafea194f6c5c2f9e146de01000d847900af7","tid":947703,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a21c88726811e1c599a3faa1b09a9c9b94630f","t